<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/People%27s_Crusade" title="People's Crusade">People's</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/First_Crusade" title="First Crusade">First</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Second_Crusade" title="Second Crusade">Second</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Third_Crusade" title="Third Crusade">Third</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Livonian_Crusade" title="Livonian Crusade">Livonian</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Crusade_of_1197" title="Crusade of 1197">German</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Fourth_Crusade" title="Fourth Crusade">Fourth</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><strong class="selflink">Albigensian</strong>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Children%27s_Crusade" title="Children's Crusade">Children's</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Fifth_Crusade" title="Fifth Crusade">Fifth</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Prussian_Crusade" title="Prussian Crusade">Prussian</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sixth_Crusade" title="Sixth Crusade">Sixth</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Seventh_Crusade" title="Seventh Crusade">Seventh</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Shepherds%27_Crusade" title="Shepherds' Crusade">Shepherds'</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Eighth_Crusade" title="Eighth Crusade">Eighth</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ninth_Crusade" title="Ninth Crusade">Ninth</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Aragonese_Crusade" title="Aragonese Crusade">Aragonese</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Alexandrian_Crusade" title="Alexandrian Crusade">Alexandrian</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Nicopolis" title="Battle of Nicopolis">Nicopolis</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Northern_Crusades" title="Northern Crusades">Northern</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hussite_Wars" title="Hussite Wars">Hussite</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Crusade_of_Varna" title="Crusade of Varna">Varna</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ottoman_invasion_of_Otranto" title="Ottoman invasion of Otranto">Otranto</a>&#160;–</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/