<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://users.erols.com/mwhite28/warstat0.htm#Crusades" class="external text" title="http://users.erols.com/mwhite28/warstat0.htm#Crusades" rel="nofollow">European Wars, Tyrants, Rebellions and Massacres (800-1700 CE)</a></li>
